		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Capital&lt;/span&gt;- Raipur&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;State bird&lt;/span&gt;- Hill myna&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;State&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;animal&lt;/span&gt;- Wild Buffalo&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;State&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;tree&lt;/span&gt;- Sal&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;State&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;flower&lt;/span&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;&lt;em&gt;Rhynchostylis&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;em&gt;gigantea&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;State&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Parks&lt;/span&gt;- Guru Ghasidas National Park, Indravati National Park, Kanger Valley National Park&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Helium.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Helium&lt;/strong&gt; is a noble gas,&lt;strong&gt; not a halogen&lt;/strong&gt;. It belongs to &lt;strong&gt;Group 18&lt;/strong&gt; of the periodic table, which includes the noble gases.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;halogens belong to Group 17 &lt;/strong&gt;of the periodic table, which includes&lt;strong&gt; fluorine, chlorine, bromine, iodine, and astatine&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Helium is a &lt;strong&gt;colourless, odourless, tasteless, non-toxic, inert, monatomic gas&lt;/strong&gt; that heads the noble gas series in the periodic table.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Unlike helium, which is unreactive due to having a full outer electron orbital, halogens are highly reactive nonmetallic elements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
